title: Led Zeppelin - 1969.03.17 Gladsaxe, Denmark
description:
Led Zeppelin - 1969.03.17 Gladsaxe, Denmark   

MARCH 17 - TV BYEN/DENMARKS RADIO/DANISH BROADCASTING CORPORATION, 
GLADSAXE, COPENHAGEN, DENMARK (MONDAY, afternoon recording session)

Aired on Danish TV, May 19, 1969 (Saturday) and "Arena Heavy Metal", 
BBC2 on January 1, 1990. Fragments were used on "Over The Hills And 
Far Away" (late 1990) and "Whole Lotta Love" (1997) promo videos. 
Finally, the whole video was used for DVD in 2003.

Tracklist:
01 - Communication Breakdown
02 - Dazed And Confused
03 - Babe I'm Gonna Leave You
04 - How Many More Times

Comments: 
This is a great mini-show performed for a small television audience.
There is an incredible amount of energy packed into this set and the 
improvisations showcase the immense talents of the band ... a great 
one to have!
